log 要比錢買 同埋你預左影相垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我99.9999% 拍片 0.0001% 影相會買gh5<br />\n<br />\n其餘情況a6500</blockquote><br />\n水貨都係萬二</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大佬用行貨價a6500 比水貨GH5 其實無咩好比..."},{"pid":"471e5adff285744d7ac7114f845cf91dd5eda9eb","tid":404994,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e2b8773968f24624b233d4d70edd6755f3a51ef","tid":404994,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"呢個價位，A7II"},{"pid":"86352a94746321a2f359cbb9bf119cd235e7ec45","tid":404994,"uid":123196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個價位，A7II</blockquote><br />\nA7ii拍片好麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申用緊"},{"pid":"29ffc0c75df09c92a86fe7347acf13b299c573c3","tid":404994,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"如果你好多時間都係拍片就gh5啦"},{"pid":"ae87f20a1a9e9c88a9557f7142bed267cfa2f64a","tid":404994,"uid":34779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"a6500個autofocus快過gh5好多,仲要係6K super sampling做 4K,不過a6500有rolling shutter問題"},{"pid":"b18a27cebfa35237d1b35742fc0fc0dd210fc70b","tid":404994,"uid":34779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T05:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a6500個autofocus快過gh5好多,仲要係6K super sampling做 4K,不過a6500有rolling shutter問題</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AEsSsdTKJs4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAEsSsdTKJs4&d=JCSSepq3pDacCyPCi12DSsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=82676ae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AEsSsdTKJs4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h4_nrc3MMJ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh4_nrc3MMJ4&d=JCSSepq3pDacCyPCi12DSsn%2FdpYTMnF