題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣有</blockquote><br />\n有，不過好少少"},{"pid":"3096618f620d63e0b00afde9362ea90d2a15ca1b","tid":404994,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a6500個autofocus快過gh5好多,仲要係6K super sampling做 4K,不過a6500有rolling shutter問題</blockquote><br />\ngh5 無rolling shutter 問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣有</blockquote><br />\n有，不過好少少</blockquote><br />\n其實真係 &quot;少少&quot; 少少到唔做ab test 分唔到差距<br />\n早排去日本， 我用a7r2 我friend 用gh5<br />\na7rii super35 mode 拍出黎rolling shutter gh5 明顯好啲<br />\n但如果a7rii 我拍ff mode, 基本上差唔多"},{"pid":"e6a330ac3691dff36913ae47eb70a8ababa8bb7b","tid":404994,"uid":88335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>a6500個autofocus快過gh5好多,仲要係6K super sampling做 4K,不過a6500有rolling shutter問題</blockquote><br />\nGH5 都有 5.1K oversampling for 4K"},{"pid":"008e3cb66715eb5561dbd2d488e8cafcb83c9164","tid":404994,"uid":88335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>a6500個autofocus快過gh5好多,仲要係6K super sampling做 4K,不過a6500有rolling shutter問題</blockquote><br />\ngh5 無rolling shutter 問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣有</blockquote><br />\n有，不過好少少</blockquote><br />\n其實真係 &quot;少少&quot; 少少到唔做ab test 分唔到差距<br />\n早排去日本， 我用a7r2 我friend 用gh5<br />\na7rii super35 mode 拍出黎rolling shutter gh5 明顯好啲<br />\n但如果a7rii 我拍ff mode, 基本上差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSensor 用 Global Shutter 先可以解決 rolling shutter.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/155520_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%